Definition: informal language consisting of words and expressions that are not considered appropriate for formal occasions
Example: often vituperative or vulgar; their speech was full of slang expressions
Synonyms: adj, all, informal, slangy, verb, communication, slang_expression, slang_term, non-standard_speech, language, consisting, of, words, and, expressions, that, are, not, considered, appropriate, for, formal, occasions, often, vituperative, or, vulgar, their, speech, was, full
Category: noun.communication
